

## 🌱 **"Paiso Ka Ped" (PKP) Investment Tracker MVP**

### 🔑 Key Features

| Feature                | Description                                             |
| ---------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
| 📥 Weekly SIP Entry    | Input ETF (e.g., NiftyBEES), Date, Price, Investment    |
| 🧮 PKP Avg Tracking    | Automatically recalculates average based on strategy    |
| 💰 Profit Check        | Compares LTP to PKP average, books profit when eligible |
| 📊 Ledger              | Shows all transactions (Buy/Sell) and running profit    |
| 🧾 Google Sheet Sync   | Persists all data on your Google Sheet                  |
| 📈 Charting (optional) | Visualize investment growth & profit booked             |

